Class FullUserTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • FullUserTest

  • public class FullUserTest
extends java.lang.Object
    package and import Test class for JStruct. This DNS shows styles and limits of code insert.

    General rules

    • Sequences blocks allow multiline code, ";" mandatory for all but last line.
    • Comments in "comments" properties for Classes and Methods are javadoc.
    • Comments in "comments" properties: line lenght limited to this ==========|
    • "/* * /" and "//" are allowed in Sequences in almost any place.
    • Conditions can be splitted in multilines; comments not allowed in conditions.
    • Code: fallows standard Java syntax.
    • Top level are Classes o Methods (special button to create)
    • Classes can contain Classes or Methods
    • User/local keywords (in menu:Options:Parser) are optional, i/o mandatory.

    More rules

    See comments in source or use Jstruct "Show comments - F2" option.
